<article>
  <div class="activity-box" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="150">
    <h2 class="heading-orange" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="150">Real or Fake?</h2>

    <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="150">
      How can you tell if the news you are reading is <strong>Real</strong> or <strong>Fake</strong>?
      <br /><br />
      Read the statements below and decide whether you think each one is representative of real or fake news.
      <br /><br />
      Select an answer for each statement and then check to see if you got them right.
    </p>

    <form class="jsReal-Fake" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos-delay="150">
      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The source and references used in the news article can be verified.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-1" name="choice-1" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-1" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-1" name="choice-1" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-1" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The headlines and visuals do not support the content within the article.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-2" name="choice-2" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-2" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-2" name="choice-2" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-2" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The news article provokes strong emotions and persuades the reader to take a certain stance.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-3" name="choice-3" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-3" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-3" name="choice-3" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-3" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The information is delivered in a direct, neutral, non-emotive, and clear way.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-4" name="choice-4" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-4" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-4" name="choice-4" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-4" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">A genuine incident was taken out of its context and re-written as breaking news.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-5" name="choice-5" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-5" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-5" name="choice-5" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-5" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The author’s name and their qualifications can be verified.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-6" name="choice-6" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-6" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-6" name="choice-6" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-6" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The article links to supporting research and statistics that can be found and verified.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-7" name="choice-7" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-7" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-7" name="choice-7" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-7" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The news content is strongly opinionated and can only be found in this one source.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-8" name="choice-8" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-8" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-8" name="choice-8" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-8" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The news article uses a lot of quotes and statistics that cannot be found elsewhere.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-9" name="choice-9" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-9" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-9" name="choice-9" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-9" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="radio-button-activity pad-widow">
        <p class="radio-button-activity__question">The news was published on a reputable and well-established news website.</p>

        <div class="radio-button-activity__choices">
          <input id="real-10" name="choice-10" type="radio" value="real" />
          <label for="real-10" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Real! </label>

          <input id="fake-10" name="choice-10" type="radio" value="fake" />
          <label for="fake-10" class="radio-button-activity__choice"> Fake! </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="jsCheck btn btn--orange force-centre">Check!</button>

      <p class="jsAnswerAll fail-box hide">Oops! Try answering all the questions before submitting</p>
      <p class="jsFail fail-box hide">Oops! That’s not quite right. Please read the statements carefully and try again.</p>
      <button class="jsTryAgain btn btn--white force-centre hide">Try again</button>

      <p class="success-box hide">Nice work!</p>
    </form>
</article>
